%% 3.2.1 Edit Student Profile — layered sequence diagram

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Actor as Admin
    participant UI as UI (Student Detail)
    participant SC as Controller (StudentController)
    participant SS as Service (StudentService)
    participant Repo as Repository (IRepository Student)
    participant DB as Database (SQL Server)

    UI->>SC: GET /api/Student/Get/{id}
    SC-->>UI: StudentDto (load detail)

    Actor->>UI: Tap Edit → change FullName, CampusId, etc.
    alt Required field empty (client validation)
        UI-->>Actor: Inline error — block API call
    else Form valid
        UI->>SC: PUT /api/Student/Update/{id} StudentUpdateDto
        SC->>SS: UpdateStudentAsync
        SS->>SS: Validate campus, deduplication rules
        SS->>Repo: Update entity + SaveChanges
        Repo->>DB: UPDATE Students
        SS-->>SC: StudentDto
        SC-->>UI: 200 OK
        UI-->>Actor: Toast — profile updated, switch back to read-only
    end
